Last time I did an IV drip video, a lot of people said, I heard that I was taking a Whitening Injection. So I said it then, and today I'm telling you this is a Nutritional Cocktail, not a Whitening Injection that will make you pale! On my second IV drip 💧 and let me tell you… this is not just a drip — it’s an investment in how I feel, live, and glow ✨ I’m not doing this to change my skin tone or follow some trend. This is for hydration, glow, and most importantly — to fill the gaps my body misses because of crazy schedules, skipped meals, and forgotten water bottles 🥲 No time for 10 different pills. No patience for half-absorption vitamins. This is 100% nutrients straight into my system — and my body? LOVES it. Drip 2.0 loading ✅ Health first, glow second ✨
